This CMS is free app. Use it if you like it)
No rights are protected by the law, just with shotgun.

You can change meta tags, site description and all other seo stuff in meta.php, which is located at /application/frontend/config/

As you alredy know - /application/frontend/ - is "user's" part of the site, and /application/backend/ is so-called admin panel.

25herz CMS provides basic blog fuctionality, such as creating blogs, managing them, posting comments... nothing impressing.
